New Reggie Becton is so Smooth.|ONErpm <fans@onerpm.com>|[**Reggie Becton** ""Streets""](https://onerpm.link/streets)

Imagine being this smooth. All night Ive been feeling toxic croons **Reggie Becton** on his new single [Streets](https://onerpm.link/streets). This sizzling new alt-R&B jam is a celebration of bad behavior, with enough lush instrumentation and female vocal-sampling to make Drizzy jealous. When you go to pick your sneaky link up this weekend, make sure this is playing over the speakers.

**Christon Gray** has dropped the deluxe version of his new album [Jacob](https://onerpm.link/559304777244). A play on Jacobs ladder, the album has garnered acclaim across the board, with the deluxe version sure to ignite even more interest. Make sure you tap in #onerpmfam.
This email was sent to mrjofre4_joffre@hotmail.com You received this email because you are registered with ONErpm

Since early drops like Unforgettable and his Mad About Bars freestyle, it was obvious Wewantwraiths was going to cement himself as a leading voice in the international hip-hop space. With impactful features from Unknown T, M Huncho, Goldlink, and Nafe Smallz, his debut album [Heartbroke Child](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/qGTkidIkwMi6mRzubHOjleWUmCMNAgnnLBFIhnJazpY6PehykOeXl6h0IT2YohtV8Xs9IIkCN5gmrrKk_cFXKRp1Vv8r3KhQ2qEkPvhhCzElat1WcyOeA13T0zLURcVsfMQSfy00PzIU9nvGfVHgkRMk_KaFaXCAUrygbagSGDSMNGV1F14pietncLGkep5E4gn0g_a_g2tCc4W35M1pX92MqE9S-V9FDand) feels like a call up to the National Team for the Leicester-based artist. Unique in sound and flow, Wraiths walks the line between pop smash shits (Next To Me) and life-weary bars (No Emotion, B4 IM G1) with aplomb. Its a brilliant debut from a rapper that deserves a place on your radar.

R&B Vocalist Bee-B has dropped a live recording of her song [Peace](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/eKkbpDpGkgc401lP2Zfxj7mYX5xQ09UDa08ol9ltKki27d5PbduMb_-EhV50I0O_oPhtwmbkq9UYGVy_mvxzT3m_w1qZEI66a0BvKwu-RscBGtDu0zLnwE3GNtyWwQxEd3_hBrFfxlQhccyFTzpfTiXoFZdp1-5hDRGlDWifgXmXEnP2F4-5FBEdXKu1Y3w74En952lGIbAGQQ). With jazz-infused guitar licks and some very slick drums, this song will inject some intimacy and calm into any setting. Crack open a bottle of wine tonight with your significant other, and let this one ease the mood.

The Bronx is reporting for duty. Haddy Racks new single [Still Haddy,](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/-JAsD2294fTgRaEvk8lpjJxH2D-gg1brqAmjV5aTxBfiUfxThpJ6BM534thpVC2fJ_0NXm-GlebvEWMI9l6LZH2S7Z-KRT-TvUmdMILFj95f7B3JX8zCc0XM-D2xCARkw-DMJe3k2_nafQIkfXlZVidfFy8xpMI5gNHCVIuHLaIwEOao_UqURRjUYi89iA6JDg0REgNeQ_UE) featuring Pop da don, and production from Mobb Deeps own Havoc is a stinger, with grit, lyrical intensity, and a very New York sound to match. Need a new record for the gym? Put this one on full volume.

Undungeon is now available on PS4 and Switch!|tinyBuild Games|"The gorgeous open-world action/RPG with a mind-bending sci-fi story lands on PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch
** Undungeon Transports Onto Nintendo Switch And PlayStation 4 Today
** Can you shatter the world to save the multiverse?

KYIV, Ukraine, September 29, 2022Undungeon, an interdimensional time-hopping action RPG by developer Laughing Machines and publisher tinyBuild, saves the multiverse on Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 today.

Time and space have fractured, leading to The Shiftan entanglement of dimensions and direct result of seven versions of Earth colliding together. As existence starts slowly fading away, The God of the Void creates the Herald, a messenger-warrior to enforce the gods will in the mortal world, stop The Shift, and restore the universe to its right form.

Travel the fused lands as they perish, talking to the various remaining life forms to discover what caused the tragic event. Fight off enemies from different universes using unique weapons, items, and skills in search of answers. Swap out equipment for different ways to approach battle, use different consumables along the way to recharge stamina, health, or to provide a much needed buff during combat.

Customize the Heralds body from the inside out, upgrading organs such as skin, liver, spleen, and eyes for powerful stat boosts. Gather priceless resources to increase skills and create an almighty armor. Combine organs, gear, and the Heralds core to stay one step ahead of unsettling threats, using melee and ranged attacks in intense real-time battles.

Step into the stunning pixel-art world of Undungeon, filled with scenic landscapes and bright, vivid astral projections. Scour terrains to experience all details and contrasting color aesthetics making up the dozens of different life forms across the seven Earths.

More than a video game, Undungeon is a powerful story of perseverance against all odds, said Maxim Vlad, Lead Game Designer Laughing Machines. Its an honor to expand its bright universe to Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4we can only hope the new players experiencing the Heralds journey to save the world have as much fun as we did creating it!

Taylor Girlz Are On The Rise|ONErpm <fans@onerpm.com>|#

Taylor Girlz have come to make the club jump. New single [Polygamy](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/5Hg7gifXEucRLgHg1Iu74IB9eYGhCCmMVAJz3QvlhgoW_GjN4SR45GTDbRJgTJReDCsvHWbKHZylU7_mzyHptV9rHX0rbVZ5_2fUTzMYiRGz4LQrJtazPVZaibQp2-wHylbjssC4pMUd1HsFw6TmUtOUsHR5ZbKqQTy48BuCgdByZJ3uYRLrfjZSKBqnNUi5DS9WJlmtIaDs) is a sharp, piano-driven smash that can go off in your car, or on the stages of Rolling Loud. Staccato drum-production, icy synths, and a heaping amount of self-confidence all help take this hedonistic banger to the next level. Theres a female-driven revolution in the rap game right now, and Taylor Girlz are at the forefront.

Legendary NBA 6th Man Lou Williams a.k.a LOU WILL has elevated what it means to be a baller. Finding success as a rapper with a string of high-energy singles, his latest record [Move](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/Gef5gZWPOWW2of5BoAd7mlah__dY9-fPEMbobyVqN77Sv6iAoGZQJFdi8pBqFyWfwVNMY23REF69uOCXviHX438TLwVrBa2ep9PRXZ4-F36bouFPn6Ok9nNShpxiehOsX5-Rr8oOnyQyWqBP5rgft_bdHRf2ZFkOTuqKgtZ_q9NCLj2J0FUV4SY5h4P0PykeKDo) will have you zipping towards the checkered flag. Featuring an ear-worm hook via Akeem Ali, this record deserves a spot on your workout playlist.

Miamis own Bizzy Crook is a wanted man, with a bounty of 10 BTC for the crime of dropping incredible bars. His new single [Flisci](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/CUHxIgsTQyW6Z5PRUuqwPSwIbwAsuFt4RxpmrVILs5cR4b3JQw6USyVvid8l-JknvuHNGrWpTpaH3LDjRLoDA1juCYwpV-VlVFZpdM6TJlI5CoL2P1_FGxMl0ubTzbhtVIrJ-wKRmnbH42DghI5DYW7Co2ZkgnVjn6U4aqaHp8mcw1L0PFv43ZqEr8nJDEOma4WRvg) sees his criminal alter ego escaping the trials of the game while also escaping commitment in classic HEAT fashion.

Its never easy when a good thing falls apart. Rising star Destinee Lynn is showing off her vocal ability on heartbroken new single [Stay](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/W2y6EJP3x0-Qj0DIvHqqeBx590PPoChTxiN1orS2QbLtZrTxeK_ZjApm0vasrja_cHvTYBMwSd8ZvzdkmsAoGKFeavCos21un-ZYIHGBXdLqrrYIODLS1705M_fwo8rNcbhu2EbwsVoBB9JxEt458L-gah3_3Ph78AuzhEhIit72w-gThVtaPod9t1VEKCeivMCQPRGdtzK9YcFHYT6C). Somber guitars and sadder pianos lay the groundwork for the rapper/singer to find catharsis in the middle of a breakup.

** tinyBuilds Vintage Sale is NOW ON!
As we enter Autumn, why not immerse yourself in the nostalgic feeling and play some of the best vintage titles published by tinyBuild with huge discounts on Steam!

Check out the tinyBuild Vintage Sale here! (https://store.steampowered.com/publisher/tinybuild/sale/vintage?utm_source=tinyBuild+newsletter&utm_campaign=e6c1372b84-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2022_10_25_12_11&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_3bd0dda51a-e6c1372b84-121862665&mc_cid=e6c1372b84&mc_eid=UNIQID)
Not sure where to start? Well, check out these awesome titles below. Weve got something for everyone to enjoy!

Surgeon Simulator is an over-the-top operation sim, stitching together pitch-black humour with life-saving surgery. Become Dr. Burke, a would-be surgeon with a less than conventional toolkit, as he performs procedures on patients including the Heavy from TF2! Wait is that a hammer?

Surgeon Simulator Games - up to 75% OFF (https://store.steampowered.com/app/233720/Surgeon_Simulator/?utm_source=tinyBuild+newsletter&utm_campaign=e6c1372b84-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2022_10_25_12_11&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_3bd0dda51a-e6c1372b84-121862665&mc_cid=e6c1372b84&mc_eid=UNIQID)

You are bread. Your mission, become toast! Take on all hazards to deliciousness as you head on an epic adventure in one of the the toughest games ever baked. All of the game modes (including Bagel Race) are now unlocked so there's sure to be something to suit everyone's taste!

Milo arrives on Earth to find that he's way too small, everybody's gone and a day hasn't passed since 1991! Catch hundreds of tinykin and use their unique powers to bring Milo back to his home planet and back to normal size!

A stealth/action game about a killer robot vacuum cleaner on a quest for vengeance through a 90s TV universe. Stalk your prey, hack smart devices, turn them into deadly traps and consume the blood of your enemies to unleash devastating powers.
Get these awesome deals and more while the tinyBuild Vintage Sale is on!
Hurry, the last day of the sale is Friday 28th October!

The device recently won the Red Dot Design Awarda sort of Oscar of the sector. READ MORE ROBERT Innovative Robot Helps Patients Get Out of Bed Faster By Ana Luiza Daltro The first step out of bed: this is how Danish company Life Science Robotics describes ROBERT, its comprehensive and flexible solution for rehabilitation. This innovative therapy system uses a KUKA LBR Med robot and focuses on the mobilization of the lower limbs. READ MORE Buying Guide: Choosing the Right Wheelchair By MedicalExpo What are the different types of wheelchairs? What are the selection criteria for choosing a wheelchair? Are there wheelchairs designed for sports? What special features can a wheelchair have? Find all the answers in our buying guide. What are the main characteristics of a knee orthosis? What are the different types of finger splints? What special features do certain splints and orthoses have? READ MORE A Brain Training Software to Reduce the Risk of Dementia By Abigail Saltmarsh Neuroscientist Dr. Henry Mahnck is an expert in brain plasticity and the CEO of Posit Science, the company behind BrainHQ, a brain training software to improve cognitive performance and reduce the risk of dementia. He is also involved in a new brain health program, aiming to lower dementia risk in the US by combining physical exercise, diet and possible lifestyle changes with brain training. READ MORE The Powerful Effect of EMDR Therapy to Treat Mental Health Conditions By Katherine Whelan Millions of people worldwide have benefited from the Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing (EMDR) therapy that brings recovery from mental health problems triggered by traumatic life events. It is best known for treating post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) but can help with a range of mental health conditions in people of all ages including depression, anxiety and addiction. READ MORE PRP Injections: The Treatment That Promises to Turn Back Time By Katherine Whelan Platelet Rich Plasma, known as PRP, is a natural and non-surgical treatment that uses the healing power of an individuals own blood to regenerate the skin and encourage new collagen production. The moment A-listers posted images of the bloody aftermath of their vampire facials, demand for the gory skin rejuvenation treatment surged. READ MORE The Growing Trend of Non-Surgical Cosmetic Treatments By Katherine Whelan After Platelet Rich Plasma injections, another innovative cosmetic treatment called Uvence uses the patients own cells to rejuvenate the skin, tackle wrinkles and reverse the signs of aging. The popularity of these kinds of natural treatments reflects the growing trend of people choosing non-invasive technology over face lifts and other surgical procedures. column1: I am Ann Mari Farzara the only daughter of late Fredrick Farzara My father who was a very wealthy cocoa merchant in Lome the economic capital of Togo.

My late father deposited USD7,000,000.00 in the bank before his death and i need your assistance to receive this fund for investment in your country while i come to your country and continue my education

Anticipating to receive your reply immediately for more details to receive my inheritance money into an account of your choice that will be provided to the bank where my late father deposited this money.
Thanks and God bless you for helping an orphan like me.

Featuring heavy synthetic trumpets, snare rolls, classic sample pack claps, and a punchy trap flow, we wouldnt be surprised to hear this one on an And1 Mixtape. Its a classic drop from an artist poised to reinvigorate the rap game.

If you arent on the JoeLew train, now is a good time to get onboard. His new single [Manners](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/4CQrGg_HwbMqJmpC2B6IU8Bw6MrCgGWiCgyKYj02KqJ1CGltW_M-m0-n6-H3AyFawDoPvu67c9dRa3dkTmjTiWn_rOYwyKDYAjxdMuEkPCv4qRyHEBVq1LMfAXgMoTcXPvD95h61m2BX5TPji-UATs5HZskgdqMeR5NIs43zf4E1OZmEwtqlbVH-G8W15Et_aSSYMJU) is a gem, with squirrel-soul samples complimenting the artists effortless flow. From the soft, uplifting piano to the bright drum hits, this is a record drenched in good vibes.

Savannah Dexter wont stop til shes number one. The multifaceted artist has released her latest album [Dex](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/3akz5JkQSwU76vCbpFxQRvyC8qT5xGxiE1r21Uv0o1XLgdg-f31cLnhgFxhCObqstSkIJcNy32JiHO66XbvrtwlJGxcrgsWfvsrsJsVodyG2TzyiBzqCGn5QWBxud9gJANmCwdpr9J59L4nDrmg_yOwF6_MpzBJ3LRsM4WkIJebW0vBD1mgqcoK9a1fQYX7C6Xrq). Listeners can expect to hear anthems for independent and hard-working women who are un-bothered and living their best life.. Anyone who wants to feel like a bad bitch- regardless of gender- make sure you stream Dex!

Avaaz suele enviar un mensaje a la semana, ofrecindote la oportunidad de participar de manera rpida y concreta en campaas de activismo mundial. Si has recibido este mensaje por error, o preferiras no recibir correos de Avaaz, haz clic aqu para darte de baja de la lista: https://secure.avaaz.org/page/es/unsubscribe/?v=143476&cid=47060 o enva un correo con el ttulo ""darme de baja"" a unsubscribe@avaaz.org

te escribo con un mensaje urgente: nuestro pas se est hundiendo! Podra ser una de las primeras naciones borradas del mapa por culpa del cambio climtico. Pero no nos vamos a quedar de brazos cruzados. Lucharemos! Dentro de unas horas, me dirigir a los asistentes de la conferencia sobre el clima que se celebra en Egipto para exigir un nuevo tratado internacional para eliminar gradualmente los combustibles fsiles y ayudar a los pases vulnerables a hacer frente a la devastacin climtica. Smate ya a mi llamamiento urgente a los lderes mundiales!
Estimados lderes mundiales presentes en la COP:
El cambio climtico est hundiendo las islas del Pacfico.
La adiccin del mundo al petrleo, al gas y al carbn amenaza con sepultar nuestros territorios, centmetro a centmetro, bajo las aguas de un ocano que va aumentando de temperatura.
Pero no nos quedaremos de brazos cruzados mientras nuestro hogar desaparece del mapa!

Nos hemos unido a un centenar de premios Nobel y a miles de cientficos del mundo entero parainstar a los lderes mundiales a sumarse al Tratado de No Proliferacin de Energas Fsiles e intentar conseguir as una transicin justa que nos aleje del uso de los combustibles fsiles .

Lleg la hora de hacer las paces con el planeta.De entregar a los pases vulnerables los fondos que se les deben desde hace tiempo y que necesitan para paliar las prdidas y los daos causados por los desastres derivados del cambio climtico. Y de hacer que los responsables de la contaminacin paguen por ello.

Dicen que, algn da, el ocano inundar esta tierra que es nuestro hogar. Pero te prometo que hasta que llegue ese da, seguiremos luchando.Porque si podemos salvar nuestras islas, podremos salvar el mundo.

Cobra fuerza campaa por Tratado de No Proliferacin de Combustibles Fsiles ( https://ipsnoticias.net/2022/11/cobra-fuerza-campana-por-tratado-de-no-proliferacion-de-combustibles-fosiles/ )(IPS) Islas que contribuyen menos al cambio climtico, pero estn en riesgo de desaparecer ( https://www.newtral.es/islas-riesgo-desaparecer-cambio-climatico/20211115/ )(Newtral) El Vaticano exige un Tratado de No Proliferacin de Combustibles Fsiles para proteger a las personas y al planeta ( https://fossilfueltreaty.org/vaticano )(Tratado de No Proliferacin de Combustibles Fsiles) La COP27 se enfrenta a un ao de cuentas pendientes e injusticia climtica ( https://www.nationalgeographic.es/medio-ambiente/2022/11/la-cop27-se-enfrenta-a-un-ano-de-cuentas-pendientes-e-injusticia-climatica )(National Geographic)

Avaaz es una red global de campaas de 70 millones de personas que trabaja para garantizar que las opiniones y valores de la gente en todo el planeta modelen los procesos de toma de decisiones a nivel mundial. ""Avaaz"" significa ""voz"" o ""cancin"" en muchos idiomas. Los miembros de Avaaz son de todas las naciones del mundo
column2: nuestro equipo est ubicado en 18 pases a lo largo de 6 continentes y opera en 17 idiomas. column1: Welcome to the world of Bee-B. Her debut album [Ghetto Fung-Shui](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/tLvPRNeESpNrZ6fN51slMUMyJbX63EJ9Ut2_RsLpNq6U1QWKg-cnFiGlN5Bi3NV92vd4Ie2_V--mi2v1GkbI0uECizuP3N_afmte-cFg2fJ43mAni-jcKCGtb58ZVRqyTzzr2vDrkr5JDxmpsfnrm3UVSJHGuzeuv0ap-2L0CLY8bOaNusL7dv2NysoNKwpluv85S-MUQ5hd)is emboldened R&B from an artist who sets the bar, then sets the mood. Whether its uptempo rhythms like Damn Good Reason or a slow jam like Can We?, theres a craftsmanship to each musical decision that simply puts this project ahead of its peers.

There arent many artists with more creativity and fun in their raps than Lyrics Born. From the funk of My Favorite Ghost, to the flair of Alligator Boots, New Album [Vision Board](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/37sa1bPXLsbiZosbTUiidx7RCjoUfKgO0fLvV1VPsf4Kwj0mxCLbLKNlpqX5N8ciqM4uwfji3iHLnIW7sfNuvFR4fesJJxOLrqFSkk_kOTPCiDp4wtMwoGpEc_Osy7r5NDIY8gfI3cxYl9HUDNfgzVbNJA-3s3ng7-dP1PEnHYsoR51NeIznsVW8N9UJzeNoJbWMz2Q6uPFN) is brimming with ideas. Its an exciting drop from the Bay-Area legend that deserves a listen front to back

Jersey club has invaded Florida, and it sounds amazing. Just 2 months after dropping stellar album 4 Month Binge Before Revenge, Wifisfuneral is back with [Obstacles](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/IiiDdPgAneD9U8IlgRKOwrOhpZyZMc9ub2cgGf9XnYOlQ1H27FmTXRMk-BfhPXYP27MQtHeg14F3kSVG6LTRHTCtYiizKOQZunE0FqlV2_Vt9--qGG0QJTPkemIS4GgzobHp9TutUd4c5l9tylY4Y0pWahQvRvOTJtLTJKHVeDiUpTCAoorO4R1DOzhbfX0EBwPP7X1yp8P6QQ). As it turns out, high-BPM kicks are the perfect setup for Wifis clever punch-in flows.

Destinee Lynns new single [Not A Bad Bytch](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/NttsHoEWaP0Wmrn0BJUloI-_4ErMwuEKhLHnQrMoMPc9DtsUZF8oDoNA7txGn6ax68_AJyYNkQwGjWUz4ZIZTVW_be7LTj_rWCL0Tx1jw2ccgfob4PoKRD-jtHtPsw8kteAHa7nUiz9zajK_XaV6-25_95Wc3vqjF_pq20XrGYxHxxnyztiR5Av0hQ_nnCTybOCktaH6YCPnHBk) is cold. Heavy 808s thump between sharp put-downs that will make any of this rising artists competitors take a step back. This is a must add #ONErpmfam.

View this email in your browser (https://mailchi.mp/tinybuild/time-to-try-deadside?e=c410f7dbd3)

Get DEADSIDE On Steam at 40% off (https://store.steampowered.com/app/895400/Deadside/?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=main_newsletter&utm_source=tinyBuild+newsletter&utm_campaign=14f56a6fd5-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2022_11_16_05_00&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_3bd0dda51a-14f56a6fd5-121862665)
Alex Nichiporchik here, CEO of tinyBuild

Over a year ago the team behind Deadside (https://store.steampowered.com/app/895400/Deadside/?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=main_newsletter&utm_source=tinyBuild+newsletter&utm_campaign=14f56a6fd5-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2022_11_16_05_00&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_3bd0dda51a-14f56a6fd5-121862665) joined tinyBuild, and what an exciting year it was for the community. I've always been a fan of shooters and spent way too many hours in DayZ and Rust, so working on Deadside with studio BadPixel has been a privilege.
* You spawn in an open, persistent world like DayZ
* You encounter bots and other players, contesting them for loot
* There are safe zones where you can store your loot
* Or you can build a base to have your own personal home

Unlike games like Rust or SCUM (which I both adore), Deadside has a unique raiding mechanic. You won't wake up to a raided base, since destroying other players' bases is possible only if you drop a raid token. So if you have a base, and get killed by other players, they might be able to raid you. The map will show where the raid is happening, and it's a highly concentrated, adrenaline-filled event.

Checkout the latest work in progress (https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/895400/view/3391800648160273766?utm_source=tinyBuild+newsletter&utm_campaign=14f56a6fd5-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2022_11_16_05_00&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_3bd0dda51a-14f56a6fd5-121862665) and ""FOLLOW"" the game on Steam
The game is 40% off until November 21, so now is a great time to check it out. Or simply click that Wishlist button so you get notifications when it's on sale.

Phresher may have just released the most-fun record of the year. Driven by a cheeky whistling melody and some wonderfully choppy drum production, [Slap](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/1e89jdCJZTrPIW1jlAF8wE39YkNH86MirsqkCLrvoKIZXatKXHHUyMDZWB6mRXhZpINLM9uUXxgPdAXDRIZYx-0OgSPrRW9jm6QJPTTbfdhMNb1qEEx-R1ETsirdveH0jsJQNJ03IpoKC8OXS7yxrnvgFQqLGKuLSjOkl0Pbu5F2gbK4oE-DkIwSXm8KsgCA3Y8) will instantly put a smile on your face. Expect this one to ring loud at every college house party as we move into the new year.

Wix Pattons new single [John Wix](http://r.fanmail.onerpm.com/mk/cl/f/0OosCGqYnsoPXZ48JOR2_rgB7lZ7_YMku7gDoT9hdlMPTdRJjNsuuFcigGTaoKkfz6ow_YXO9-L-2vjSRwM6VTJLsZIV2H694z7eebmMxIDrx_g4yl8yqNULE8byVFzDkAXjZfEtfBGWgjJZIqYu-RByAPlLN2eykHFrSSoaW5FR2u5WPD8Aa068sSSxt5B4QvbVRbs) is an adept and versatile single that highlights the artists ability to adopt different styles in one record. An open and atmospheric beat leaves plenty of space for Wix to shine, making this single another W in a string of recent bangers.

Have you tried the touch-optimized taskbar yet?|"Windows Insider Program"" <windowsinsiderprogram@e-mail.microsoft.com>"|"
Windows Insider ProgramPlus, discover the Windows 11 security and snap layout insights. |
Touch-optimized taskbar in the Dev Channel and Beta Channel

The touch-optimized taskbar feature is now available to all Windows Insiders in the Dev Channel (Build 25231) and Beta Channel (Build 22623.875). Your taskbar will automatically transition to the optimized version for tablet when you disconnect or fold back the keyboard on your 2-in-1 device.
See how it works in our webcast
Easier to stay safe with Windows 11 Security

Windows 11 is the most secure version of Windows yet. Go behind the scenes to learn about some Windows 11 security features like Smart App Control, enhanced phishing protection and memory integrity. Its important for security to be invisible so you can focus on using your PC without fear.
Windows Insiders helped us improve snap layouts

Snap layouts on Windows 11 have been a game changer for multitasking. Thanks to the Windows Insiders feedback, snap layouts now work with both touch and mouse. Check out the inside story to learn how and why we made these improvements.
Play the snap layouts and touch video
Windows Search and our plans through the end of 2022
Try the Pen Focused View in OneNote

Create with your pen in OneNote without distractions and use all your favorite customized pen tools to take notes, doodle, or brainstorm with the Pen Focused View. Mouse and touch users can use it as well!
Learn more about the Pen Focused View
Get inspired with templates and tips from the ultimate creator launchpad

Microsoft Create brings together the power of its content creation apps, from PowerPoint to Word to Clipchamp, to help you express your creativity. Discover professional quality templates and uplevel your creative skills with curated tips from expert creators.
Watch Microsoft Technical Takeoff: Windows and Microsoft Intune sessions

If you missed the Microsoft Technical Takeoff event in October, watch the recordings of demos, deep dives and Ask Microsoft Anything sessions on the latest features, capabilities and scenarios for Windows, Microsoft Intune and more.
Ever accidentally copied over text on your clipboard?
With clipboard history enabled you dont need to worryall the latest text and pictures youve copied are still accessible.
Wish it was easier to move the text cursor with touch?
When using the touch keyboard, press and hold on space and then slide your fingerthe text cursor will follow!
Do you convert between certain time zones a lot?
You can add up to two clocks to the taskbars clock and calendar flyout! Just go to Date & Time in Settings.
The Clock app can help too
